reviews.text: The clearly visible Eftpos machine was ‘magically not working’, he refused to accept card and only accepted cash. This is one of the few vendors selling the SG Tourist Pass (Red) - given the tourist pass is a government initiative to promote tourism, this is not very tourist friendly. Shame.
